{"type":"answer","id":149377,"parentType":"question","parentId":17179,"uid":20551,"contents":"你共舆论战的常规操作：先造谣，再辟谣，反向加速异议群体。<br>\n<br>\n<b>先造谣，故意容忍一部分反贼言论，把风向带起来。</b><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ENZXJbA.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ENZXJbA.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ENZXJbA.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>然后辟谣，借此抹黑反贼群体的形象，收割一波中立人士。</b><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/sU8w1pn.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sU8w1pn.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/sU8w1pn.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>看画框部分</b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/bFfyW54.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bFfyW54.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/bFfyW54.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n对策：发表评论前，新闻要FC(fact checking，即核实)，防止被反向加速。<s>也可以编造各种中又赢的fake news，去加速小粉红</s>","date":"2020-02-03","agreeCount":20,"discussionCount":6}